Hi {!Background_check__c.Volunteer__c},

Our records indicate your last criminal background check was conducted three years ago. Our Governing Policies, Performance Standards and Guidelines require all staff, board members, and volunteers who “have either direct contact with children, access to confidential information, or access to chapter funds” to submit to a criminal background check every three years. In order to keep your "ACTIVE" volunteer status, please log in to the Make-A-Wish Volunteer Center to initiate your background check.


Please ensure that you have completed the requested information by {!Background_check__c.Date__c}. After this date, your access to the Volunteer Center will be disabled and you will no longer be able to access your current assignments, future opportunities or valuable resources. If you prefer to be put on “INACTIVE” status now, please log in and change your status accordingly or email our team and we are happy to make this adjustment on your behalf.


Thank you so much for your attention to this important matter. We are grateful for your continued support of our mission and the children we serve! Because of you, wishes come true!


Thanks,

